to the concepts in this.

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:45.650
I'm not going to be reading
from the book or anything.

00:01:45.650 --> 00:01:47.760
But I'll be speaking
to this quite a bit.

00:01:47.760 --> 00:01:50.510
The focus on the book is
really around meditation

00:01:50.510 --> 00:01:52.610
and mindfulness, my
experience with it.

00:01:52.610 --> 00:01:55.690
I've been practicing meditation
for about 20 years, mindfulness

00:01:55.690 --> 00:01:58.450
for probably about 12 years.

00:01:58.450 --> 00:02:00.300
